game.name: Queen Fashion Magazine Cover
game.description:
It is seriously a big day in the life of Elsa when her long awaited dream is going to come true! Yes, a very popular fashion magazine has appointed her as a model and they will put her picture on their cover page. As a result, the lady looks pretty excited and does not want to compromise on her final look. Would you join her to make her look that is worth seeing on the fashion magazine? Join Queen Fashion Magazine Cover and be prepared to help the princess pick up an outfit for a fashion model!
After making experiments with her look, you also have to take photos that she has given to the magazine. Your primary objective in this brand new dressing game for girls is to guide Elsa to choose a trendy dress. Enter this game and get ready to play the role of fashion stylist who can transform a simple looking-girl into the most gorgeous one! First, give her a nice make-up with the help of eyelashes, lipstick, blushes, and also change the color of her eyes! 
After doing her makeover, get ready to work on her outfit. Give her a nice handbag, a suitable goggle, an elegant hairstyle and a lovely outfit in this one of the best html5 princess games! Do not forget to complete her look with a matching hat, a pair of shoes, sparkling jewelry, and a pair of earrings. Once you are done, click the right click button to see the final result. We are happy to offer the high-quality kids makeover games that are playable online, no download required.
